---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

<Layout
  title="Fractional Advisory Studio — Strategic Advisory by Nikki Cates"
  description="Three tiers of liberation-centered strategic advisory for women navigating structural strain in the AI era — group intensives, premium 1:1 engagements, and fractional executive advisory."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[78vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-st-gradient"></div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 82% 32%, rgba(13,148,136,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);"
    ></div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.08]"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"
    ></div>
    <div
      class="absolute right-[-6rem] top-20 h-64 w-64 rotate-12 border border-teal-DEFAULT/20"
      style="clip-path: polygon(25% 6.7%, 75% 6.7%, 100% 50%, 75% 93.3%, 25% 93.3%, 0% 50%);"
    ></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-teal-DEFAULT"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Strategic Transformations</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1">
            URI-rooted leadership architecture
          </span>
        </div>
       <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-light font-bold leading-tight mb-6 animate-on-scroll">
  Fractional Advisory Studio
</h1>
          The Fractional Strategic Advisory Studio
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-light text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-4 animate-on-scroll"
          style="animation-delay:0.08s"
        >
          Three tiers of liberation-centered strategic advisory — for women navigating over-responsibility, structural strain, and the AI era without a system built for their sustainability.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-8 animate-on-scroll"
          style="animation-delay:0.12s"
        >
          This is not coaching. Not consulting. It is strategic architecture rooted in the Unmasking Restore Intelligence (URI) framework — designed to help you name what is structural, recover what has been hidden, and move forward with clarity, boundaries, and a plan that does not cost you your nervous system.
        </p>
        <div class="mb-8 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.16s">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted mb-2">
            A Strategic Transformations diagnostic and advisory experience
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-light">
            Access is curated. Tier 1 and Tier 3 engagements are by invitation only.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
          <a href="#tier-overview" class="btn-teal">Find your tier</a>
          <a href="#inquiry-form" class="btn-outline-teal">Go to the inquiry form</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIER OVERVIEW -->
  <section id="tier-overview" class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Three engagement tiers</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-4">
          One lane. Three levels of depth.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Each tier is designed with clear boundaries, curated access, and intentional capacity limits. Not every engagement will be the right fit — and that is by design.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Tier 0 · Open Enrollment</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-2xl mb-3">Strategic Reset Intensive</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">
            A curated small-group cohort for women navigating burnout, over-responsibility, and AI-era strain. One reset. Real tools. Clear next steps.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mb-5 space-y-1">
            <p class="text-light text-sm"><span class="text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold">$247</span> · Group cohort</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm"><span class="text-light">$997</span> · VIP add-on available</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-2">One cohort per quarter · Next: <span class="text-light">May 21</span></p>
          </div>
          <a href="#tier-0" class="btn-teal w-full text-center text-sm">See Tier 0 details</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll flex flex-col" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Tier 1 · By Invitation</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-2xl mb-3">Premium Intensive</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">
            A private, deep-dive intensive for women who need more than a group reset — personalized strategic architecture, decision clarity, and execution support.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mb-5 space-y-1">
            <p class="text-light text-sm"><span class="text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold">$6,500</span> · Base intensive</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">+ Follow-up: $1,500 · Team workshop: $3,500</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-2">Two slots per month maximum</p>
          </div>
          <a href="#tier-1" class="btn-outline-teal w-full text-center text-sm">See Tier 1 details</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll flex flex-col" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Tier 3 · By Invitation</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-2xl mb-3">Fractional Strategic Advisory</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">
            Ongoing embedded advisory for organizations navigating structural change, leadership transitions, and AI-era complexity — from the inside.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mb-5 space-y-1">
            <p class="text-light text-sm"><span class="text-teal-DEFAULT font-semibold">$10K–$20K</span> · Monthly retainer</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">Segmented by org stage and sector</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-2">One client at a time</p>
          </div>
          <a href="#tier-3" class="btn-outline-teal w-full text-center text-sm">See Tier 3 details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIER 0 -->
  <section id="tier-0" class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 20% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-8 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Tier 0 · Open Enrollment</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-teal-DEFAULT border border-teal-DEFAULT/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
          Strategic Reset Intensive
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start mb-16">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-6">
            A Strategic Reset Intensive for women who refuse to be the
            <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT italic">load-bearing wall</span>
            of the AI era.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            This is a curated small-group cohort for women navigating over-responsibility, under-support, and the pressure to keep performing in systems that were never designed for their sustainability.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You will leave with a personal AI governance boundary, a practical AI operating system, and an execution plan that turns uncertainty into movement — without sacrificing your nervous system, your integrity, or your voice.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
            A limited VIP add-on is available for women who want private follow-up, tailored application, or a deeper 1:1 reset after the group intensive.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
          {[
            { tag: 'Phase 1', title: 'Diagnostic Pre-Work', desc: 'A short intake and reflection process to surface burnout patterns, authority mismatch, hidden labor, masking pressure, and AI strain before the live intensive.' },
            { tag: 'Phase 2', title: 'Live Group Reset', desc: 'One 2-hour strategic small-group intensive designed to help participants name structural strain, clarify current reality, and identify the highest-leverage moves forward.' },
            { tag: 'Phase 3', title: 'Reset Tools', desc: 'A practical reset framework including AI boundaries, execution priorities, and next-step prompts you can use immediately after the session.' },
            { tag: 'Included', title: 'UNMASK Blueprint Vol. 1', desc: 'Deconstruction of the Grind, including the accompanying interactive web experience.' },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="p-5 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors bg-surface/50">
              <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-2">{item.tag}</p>
              <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-lg mb-2">{item.title}</p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Cohort dates + pricing -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mb-10 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/30 bg-teal-DEFAULT/5">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-5">Upcoming Cohort Dates</p>
          <div class="space-y-5 mb-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-teal-DEFAULT/10 border border-teal-DEFAULT/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs font-bold">Q2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">May 21, 2025</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm">Spring cohort — limited seats</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-md bg-teal-DEFAULT/10 border border-teal-DEFAULT/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs font-bold">Q3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">August 20, 2025</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm">Summer cohort — limited seats</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-xs">One cohort per quarter. Each cohort is small by design. Seats are not guaranteed until enrollment is confirmed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-border">
          <p class="text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-5">Investment</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-5">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">Group Cohort</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm">Full cohort experience + reset tools + UNMASK Blueprint</p>
              </div>
              <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">$247</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">VIP Add-On</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm">Group cohort + private follow-up + tailored 1:1 application</p>
              </div>
              <p class="font-heading text-teal-DEFAULT text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">$997</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-xs">Payment link shared after fit confirmation. One-cohort-per-quarter limit applies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="#inquiry-form" data-tier="0" class="btn-teal cta-tier-btn">Apply for the May Cohort</a>
        <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-3 max-w-md">Applications reviewed on a rolling basis. Not every inquiry will be advanced. This is a protected entry point, not an open marketplace.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIER 1 -->
  <section id="tier-1" class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 80% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-10 p-4 rounded-md border border-teal-DEFAULT/20 bg-teal-DEFAULT/5 max-w-3xl animate-on-scroll">
        <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-1">Protected Access</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
          Tier 1 is available by invitation only. If you have been directed here by Nikki or a trusted referral, the inquiry form below is your right next step. This offering is not listed as an open-access service.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-8 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Tier 1 · By Invitation</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-teal-DEFAULT border border-teal-DEFAULT/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
          Premium Intensive
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start mb-16">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-6">
            A private deep-dive for women who need more than a reset.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Premium Intensive is a high-proximity, single-session engagement designed for women navigating complex leadership transitions, organizational strain, or strategic pivots that require more precision than a group format can provide.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            This is personalized strategic architecture — not a coaching call, not a one-size-fits-all framework. You will leave with a clear diagnostic, a decision framework, and a next-step plan built for your specific context.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Two slots available per month. This is not a marketing tactic. It is a capacity boundary that protects the quality of every engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
          {[
            { title: 'Premium Intensive', pricing: '$6,500', desc: 'The core engagement. A private, intensive session with customized pre-work, deep diagnostic, and a personalized execution architecture.' },
            { title: 'Follow-Up Session', pricing: '$1,500 add-on', desc: 'A private follow-up session for participants who need strategic check-in, course correction, or continued accountability after the intensive.' },
            { title: 'Team Workshop', pricing: '$3,500 add-on', desc: 'An organizational extension workshop to bring strategic clarity and shared language to your leadership team or direct reports.' },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="p-5 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors bg-surface/50">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-lg">{item.title}</p>
                <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">{item.pricing}</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
          <div class="p-4 rounded-md bg-teal-DEFAULT/5 border border-teal-DEFAULT/20">
            <p class="text-muted text-xs">Two Tier 1 engagements per month maximum. Add-ons available exclusively to current Tier 1 participants. Payment and intake details shared after fit is confirmed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="#inquiry-form" data-tier="1" class="btn-outline-teal cta-tier-btn">Request Premium Intensive Details</a>
        <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-3">By invitation only. Inquiries reviewed before any engagement details are shared.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TIER 3 -->
  <section id="tier-3" class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-10 p-4 rounded-md border border-teal-DEFAULT/20 bg-teal-DEFAULT/5 max-w-3xl animate-on-scroll">
        <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-1">Protected Access</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">
          Tier 3 is available by referral and invitation only. This is a one-client-at-a-time advisory relationship and is not listed as an open-access service. If you have been directed here by Nikki or a trusted source, the inquiry form is your right next step.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-8 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Tier 3 · By Invitation</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-teal-DEFAULT border border-teal-DEFAULT/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
          Fractional Strategic Advisory
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start mb-16">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-6">
            Embedded advisory for organizations navigating structural change from the inside.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Fractional Strategic Advisory is an ongoing embedded relationship — not a retainer for periodic advice, but a sustained presence inside your organizational decision-making structure. Nikki works alongside leadership to name what is structural, recover what has been hidden, and build systems that don't depend on one person's overfunctioning to hold together.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            This engagement is rooted in the URI framework — a liberation-centered architecture for organizational change that centers sustainability, equity, and structural honesty rather than performance and speed.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
            One client at a time. This is not a scalability play. It is a commitment to depth.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
          <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex">Monthly Retainer Segments</span>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
            {[
              {
                segment: 'Early Stage / Nonprofit',
                price: '$10,000',
                desc: 'For mission-driven organizations, early-stage companies, and nonprofits navigating structural transition with limited executive bandwidth.',
              },
              {
                segment: 'Growth / Mid-Size',
                price: '$15,000',
                desc: 'For growing organizations that have outpaced their structural foundation and need embedded advisory to stabilize, reorient, and build with more integrity.',
              },
              {
                segment: 'Corporate / Enterprise',
                price: '$20,000',
                desc: 'For larger organizations navigating complex structural change, leadership misalignment, or AI-era disruption at scale.',
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="p-5 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors bg-surface/50">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                  <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">{item.segment}</p>
                  <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT font-bold text-lg flex-shrink-0">
                    {item.price}<span class="text-muted text-xs font-normal">/mo</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-md bg-teal-DEFAULT/5 border border-teal-DEFAULT/20">
            <p class="text-muted text-xs">One Tier 3 client at a time. Pricing is segmented by organizational stage and sector, not deliverable volume. Engagement terms shared during fit conversation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <a href="#inquiry-form" data-tier="3" class="btn-teal cta-tier-btn">Inquire About Strategic Advisory</a>
        <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-3">By referral and invitation only. Inquiries screened before engagement details are shared.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INQUIRY FORM -->
  <section id="inquiry-form" class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-10 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Protected Entry Point</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-4">
          Fractional Lane Studio Inquiry
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
          This is the first step for all three tiers. Select the offering you are inquiring about, then complete the form. Every submission is reviewed individually before any next steps are shared.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Tier 1 and Tier 3 inquiries are only advanced if you have been personally directed here. If this is your first point of contact with this work, Tier 0 is likely your best starting place.
        </p>
      </div>

      <form id="fractional-form" class="space-y-10" novalidate>

        <!-- 00: TIER SELECTION -->
        <fieldset class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/20">
          <legend class="font-heading text-light text-xl font-semibold mb-1 px-2">
            00 — Which Offering Are You Inquiring About?
          </legend>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6 px-2">Select one. Your choice personalizes the questions that follow.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            {[
              { value: '0', label: 'Tier 0 · Strategic Reset Intensive', desc: 'Group cohort · $247 / $997 VIP · Open enrollment' },
              { value: '1', label: 'Tier 1 · Premium Intensive', desc: 'Private intensive · $6,500 base · By invitation' },
              { value: '3', label: 'Tier 3 · Fractional Advisory', desc: 'Embedded advisory · $10K–$20K/mo · By invitation' },
            ].map((tier) => (
              <label
                class="tier-option flex flex-col gap-1 p-4 bg-surface border border-border rounded-md text-sm cursor-pointer hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors"
                data-tier-value={tier.value}
              >
                <input
                  type="radio"
                  name="selectedTier"
                  value={tier.value}
                  class="sr-only tier-radio"
                  required
                />
                <span class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-base">{tier.label}</span>
                <span class="text-muted text-xs">{tier.desc}</span>
              </label>
            ))}
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <!-- 01: CONTACT -->
        <fieldset class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/20">
          <legend class="font-heading text-light text-xl font-semibold mb-1 px-2">
            01 — Contact + Current Season
          </legend>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6 px-2">Tell me who you are and what season you are in.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label" for="full-name">Full Name *</label>
              <input class="form-input" id="full-name" name="fullName" type="text" placeholder="Your full name" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label" for="email">Email Address *</label>
              <input class="form-input" id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
            </div>
            <div id="org-name-group" class="form-group md:col-span-2" style="display:none;">
              <label class="form-label" for="org-name">Organization Name</label>
              <input class="form-input" id="org-name" name="orgName" type="text" placeholder="Your organization or company name" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group md:col-span-2">
              <label class="form-label" for="current-season">Current Role / Season *</label>
              <select class="form-select" id="current-season" name="currentSeason" required>
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option>employed professional</option>
                <option>senior leader / executive</option>
                <option>founder / business owner</option>
                <option>nonprofit leader / director</option>
                <option>in transition</option>
                <option>currently unemployed / re-entering</option>
                <option>other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

